    <h1>Custom Gown Design and Consultation Services</h1>

    <h2>Scope of Services</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Consultation and Design:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Determine your preferred style and budget for your custom gown.</li>
                <li>Schedule a consultation to discuss your vision with our designer, Mimi.</li>
                <li>Optional $30 sketch design (non-refundable).</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Design Concept and Approval:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Attend a Zoom consultation to finalize your design details.</li>
                <li>Receive a final sketch of your gown for approval (optional, $30 fee).</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Fabric Selection:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Receive curated fabric options tailored to your style and budget.</li>
                <li>Select your fabrics and make a deposit (50% of total cost) within two weeks.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Fabric Procurement and Payment:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Fabric delivery typically takes 2-3 weeks.</li>
                <li>Receive images and videos of fabrics upon arrival.</li>
                <li>Make a 50% down payment before fabric purchase (non-refundable).</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Fittings and Adjustments:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Schedule first and second fittings (4-6 weeks apart).</li>
                <li>Discuss any changes or additions during fittings.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Payment Schedule:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Pay 50% of remaining balance at the last fitting.</li>
                <li>Final balance due one week before pick-up or at pick-up.</li>
                <li>Optional: Make payments throughout the process.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Appointment Timeliness:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Be punctual for appointments (late fees apply).</li>
                <li>Receive notification of any appointment changes (one week's notice).</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Delivery:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Receive free shipping on your custom-made gown.</li>
                <li>Gown will be carefully packaged and delivered to your specified location (delivery fee paid separately).</li>
                <li>Pick-up options available.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>

